Tournaments & Outings
Cypress Head Golf Club specializes in hosting memorable golf tournaments and group outings. Whether you’re planning a fundraiser or a corporate event, our team will collaborate with your committee and volunteers to tailor the perfect event for your group. We ensure that every detail is taken care of, making your event a success for players, guests, and sponsors.
Contact Leslie House to book a golf event:
[email protected]
.
And if you’re looking for a fun way to give back, join us for an event that supports local organizations and makes a meaningful impact in the community. Register to play and sponsor any of our listed events on this page.
